- The total time is calculated by summing the time taken by the athlete in all events they participated in;
- The total medals include gold, silver, and bronze medals won by the athlete.

- 'Shining stars' refers to athletes with the highest total scores;
- 'Lead the pack' refers to teams with the highest total scores;
- 'Presence' refers to the number of access events by the user (athlete);
- 'Performance within their respective classes' refers to the average rank of athletes in their class levels.

