- `class_name` is the name given to each class level;
- The `COUNT` function counts the number of athletes in each class level;
- The `MAX` function finds the highest class ID;
- The `GROUP BY` clause groups the results by class name;
- The `ORDER BY` clause sorts the results in descending order by the count of athletes.
